{"tid":247783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袋鼠亂入澳洲賽馬場挑機","createTime":"2017-05-18T05:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T12:27:01.000Z","uid":54373,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13f12bdeb7dae04f738ad7af4ed5553656df2f8e","tid":247783,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"澳洲一場賽馬比賽上，一只袋鼠成了全場的焦點。這隻亂入的袋鼠與賽道上馬匹乎並駕齊驅，速度之快令人驚奇！<br />\n<br />\n領先的騎師李善利(Serg Lisnyy)表示他在騎到一半時，這隻袋鼠突然從草叢跳入賽道，還跟著馬群跑了150米才離開。李善利又話袋鼠與他的坐騎非常接近，還是第一次遇到袋鼠向他挑戰，令讓他感到又嬲又好笑。<br />\n<br />\n幸好這個不速之客沒有造成騎師及馬匹受傷。目擊的馬夫Danny Greer表示通常即使有袋鼠走入馬場，都會因為懼怕馬群而走開。不過這隻袋鼠就跟住大隊跑，非常罕見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2017/05/20170510_upower_%E8%A2%8B%E9%BC%A02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2017%2F05%2F20170510_upower_%25E8%25A2%258B%25E9%25BC%25A02.jpg&h=315c9bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2017/05/20170510_upower_%E8%A2%8B%E9%BC%A03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2017%2F05%2F20170510_upower_%25E8%25A2%258B%25E9%25BC%25A03.jpg&h=fdf69b26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2017/05/20170510_upower_%E8%A2%8B%E9%BC%A04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2017%2F05%2F20170510_upower_%25E8%25A2%258B%25E9%25BC%25A04.jpg&h=f733923f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2db87eaaff656c605e97a7ade74bae6ccf9c191","tid":247783,"uid":7458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好得意"},{"pid":"748b560eed9645ba86694bef557ec0494b4c61dc","tid":247783,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:32